title: Modway Ernie Mid-Century Modern Wood Bar Stool in Walnut
features: MID-CENTURY MODERN STOOL - Polished chrome detail and wood grain accents harmonize to create this retro bar stool. The fluid lines and V-shaped back will instantly elevate your home bar dining décor
VERSATILE DESIGN - A welcome addition to the bar table, kitchen island, or bar-height counter, this versatile mid-century modern bar stool complements your home, apartment, or small living space
STURDY CONSTRUCTION - Sitting atop sleek metal legs with a stylish, functional footrest, the solid plywood seat on this stool offers comprehensive support with its waterfall edge and winged backrest
MODERN BAR STOOL MEASUREMENTS - Complement a variety of décors from retro modern to contemporary with this stylish stool. Includes non-marking caps. Dimensions: 18.5"L x 22.5"W x 45.5"H
description: Minimalist in nature though it may be, the Ernie Bar Stool doesn't skimp on comfort. Its seemingly rigid design, flexes to the contours of the human body, making it a great bar stool for dining and home office use. The Ernie Bar Stool is sturdily constructed of plywood and supported by polished chrome legs.
